                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390513-name-198" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390513-name-198" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390513-name-198" type="surname" value="WHITTON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390513-name-198" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN WHITTON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a woollen-draper in Tottenham Court-road. I have a partner—the prisoner was at work in my shop as a journeyman painter—on the 13th of April I missed a piece of satin, and found it in pledge—I went to the prisoner's lodging, and took him in bed.</p>
